<span class="line"><span style="color:#56B6C2;">-</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">F, </span><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">--</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">list-</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">formats               列出每个视频的可用格式。模拟除非使用</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">-</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">no</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">-</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;"> simulation</span></span>
