<span class="line"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">--</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">no</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">-</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">embed</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">-</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">thumbnail             </span><span style="color:#61AFEF;">不嵌入缩略图</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">(默认)</span></span>
